14:23.738 --> 14:25.114
that you're

14:23.738 --> 14:25.114
a great detective.

14:25.156 --> 14:26.658
That's why you set

14:25.156 --> 14:26.658
this whole thing up.

14:26.700 --> 14:28.284
It was a perfect plan,

14:28.326 --> 14:29.786
