Tell them how much

14:46.386 --> 14:47.679
our accountant hates me.

14:47.721 --> 14:49.013
She hates him so much.

14:49.055 --> 14:50.390
My bag was sitting

14:49.055 --> 14:50.390
next to my desk.

14:50.431 --> 14:52.016
Anyone could have

14:50.431 --> 14:52.016
