and that was because

14:56.020 --> 14:57.564
I made a terrific joke.

14:57.605 --> 14:59.273
I was there.

14:57.605 --> 14:59.273
It was hilarious.

14:59.315 --> 15:00.525
Come on.

15:00.567 --> 15:02.610
I guess it's fair to say

15:00.567 --> 15:02.610
case closed.

15:02.652 --> 15:03.862
No.

15:02.652 --> 15:03.862
He stole that from me.

15:03.903 --> 15:05.238
[Holt] Go home.

15:05.279 --> 15:07.407
You're suspended

15:05.279 --> 15:07.407
until further notice.

15:07.448 --> 15:08.616
This is nuts.

15:08.658 --> 15:10.159
I can't believe

15:08.658 --> 15:10.159
Holt believes

15:10.201 --> 15:12.370
that ridiculous windbag

15:10.201 --> 15:12.370
and his sack of lies.

15:12.412 --> 15:14.955
Oh, I know everything about

15:12.412 --> 15:14.955
glitter and "Drake's Elbow."

15:14.997 --> 15:16.416
-"Hollow."

15:14.997 --> 15:16.416
-Amy, please.

15:16.457 --> 15:18.626
I just need your support

15:16.457 --> 15:18.626
right now, okay?

15:18.668 --> 15:20.086
Wait a minute,

15:18.668 --> 15:20.086
you believe me, right?

15:20.127 --> 15:21.880
Of course I do.

15:20.127 --> 15:21.880
I'm your wife.

15:21.921 --> 15:23.297
I'm on your side

15:21.921 --> 15:23.297
