15:23.339 --> 15:24.591
[sighs]

15:23.339 --> 15:24.591
Thanks.

15:24.632 --> 15:26.050
-Same, by the way.

15:24.632 --> 15:26.050
-Thanks.

15:26.092 --> 15:27.510
I mean,

15:26.092 --> 15:27.510
no one really suspects me.

15:27.552 --> 15:29.095
-Right.

15:27.552 --> 15:29.095
-Look, go home.

15:29.136 --> 15:31.013
I'll check for prints

15:29.136 --> 15:31.013
on the Party Zone receipt.

15:31.055 --> 15:33.391
Yours won't be there,

15:31.055 --> 15:33.391
