15:33.433 --> 15:35.602
Wait a minute.

15:33.433 --> 15:35.602
Prints--that's it.

15:35.643 --> 15:37.228
I think I know who framed me.

15:37.270 --> 15:38.855
-Who?

15:37.270 --> 15:38.855
-I can't say yet.

15:37.270 --> 15:38.855
I wanna be sure.

15:38.897 --> 15:40.106
You wanna do a big,

15:38.897 --> 15:40.106
dramatic reveal

15:40.147 --> 15:41.691
in front of everyone, don't you?

15:41.733 --> 15:43.276
Yes, obviously! Look, I have

15:41.733 --> 15:43.276
to go check on one thing.

15:43.317 --> 15:44.652
-Don't let anybody leave.

15:43.317 --> 15:44.652
-'Kay.

15:46.112 --> 15:47.447
