15:46.112 --> 15:47.447
Attention, everyone.

15:47.488 --> 15:49.490
Stop what you are doing.

15:49.532 --> 15:50.825
[normally]

15:49.532 --> 15:50.825
Eh, still a little Nazi.

15:50.867 --> 15:52.285
I'm gonna just drop the accent.

15:52.326 --> 15:54.370
Peralta, you can't be here.

15:52.326 --> 15:54.370
You're suspended.

15:54.412 --> 15:55.830
And you're lucky

15:54.412 --> 15:55.830
it's not worse.

15:55.872 --> 15:57.248
The DA's office

15:55.872 --> 15:57.248
wanted you fired.

15:57.290 --> 15:59.500
I'm being framed,

15:57.290 --> 15:59.500
